sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant AuthProxy as Auth Proxy<br/>(kube-rbac-proxy)<br/>Injected by Operator
    participant Route as OpenShift Route<br/>80/TCP HTTP
    participant Service as trustyai-service<br/>ClusterIP 80/TCP
    participant TrustyAI as TrustyAI Service<br/>8080/TCP HTTP<br/>4443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Storage as Storage Backend<br/>(PVC / MariaDB / MinIO)
    participant KServe as KServe Model Server<br/>gRPC/HTTP2
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus

    Note over Client,Prometheus: Flow 1: ModelMesh Inference Data Capture

    participant ModelMesh as ModelMesh Serving

    ModelMesh->>Service: POST /consumer/kserve/v2<br/>80/TCP HTTP, No Auth
    Service->>TrustyAI: Forward to 8080/TCP
    TrustyAI->>Storage: Persist inference data<br/>PVC: File I/O (CSV/Parquet)<br/>DB: JDBC 3306/TCP<br/>MinIO: S3 API 9000/TCP TLS
    Storage-->>TrustyAI: Write confirmed

    Note over Client,Prometheus: Flow 2: On-Demand Explanation (ODH only)

    Client->>Route: POST /explainers/local/shap<br/>80/TCP HTTP
    Route->>AuthProxy: Forward request
    AuthProxy->>TrustyAI: Authenticated request<br/>8080/TCP
    TrustyAI->>Storage: Load inference data
    Storage-->>TrustyAI: Historical data
    TrustyAI->>KServe: gRPC V2 InferRequest<br/>ModelInfer RPC<br/>Semaphore-limited concurrency
    KServe-->>TrustyAI: InferResponse<br/>Prediction results
    Note right of TrustyAI: Compute SHAP values<br/>using perturbations
    TrustyAI-->>AuthProxy: SHAP explanation JSON
    AuthProxy-->>Route: Response
    Route-->>Client: 200 OK + explanation

    Note over Client,Prometheus: Flow 3: Scheduled Metric Calculation & Publishing

    Note right of TrustyAI: Quarkus Scheduler triggers<br/>every 5s (configurable)
    TrustyAI->>Storage: Read inference data batch<br/>batch_size: 50000
    Storage-->>TrustyAI: Dataframe
    Note right of TrustyAI: Calculate SPD, DIR,<br/>KS, MMD, Meanshift
    TrustyAI->>TrustyAI: Publish Micrometer gauges<br/>trustyai_spd, trustyai_dir

    Prometheus->>Service: GET /q/metrics<br/>80/TCP HTTP<br/>Bearer Token (SA)
    Service->>TrustyAI: Forward to 8080/TCP
    TrustyAI-->>Prometheus: Prometheus exposition format<br/>trustyai_spd{model=..., feature=...}

    Note over Client,Prometheus: Flow 4: Fairness Metric Request (RHOAI)

    Client->>Route: POST /metrics/group/fairness/spd<br/>80/TCP HTTP
    Route->>AuthProxy: Forward request
    AuthProxy->>TrustyAI: Schedule SPD metric
    TrustyAI->>Storage: Read reference data
    Storage-->>TrustyAI: Dataframe
    Note right of TrustyAI: Compute SPD for<br/>protected attribute
    TrustyAI-->>AuthProxy: SPD result + schedule confirmation
    AuthProxy-->>Route: Response
    Route-->>Client: 200 OK + metric value
